# Surya Puja Page — Full Implementation Documentation

## Overview
This document describes every file created/modified to build the **Surya (Sun) Puja** individual page with a live booking system, time-slot locking, and a daily quota enforcement feature.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Navbar Dropdown\nSurya Puja link] -->|slug routing| B[/puja/surya-puja]
    B --> C[SuryaPujaPage.jsx]
    C -->|GET availability| D[Express API]
    C -->|POST booking| D
    D --> E[PujaBooking Controller]
    E --> F[MongoDB — PujaBooking Model]
```

