## Files Created

### 1. Backend — Model
**`server/models/PujaBooking.js`**

A dedicated Mongoose schema (separate from the generic `Appointment` model) with:

| Field | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `pujaId` | String | Identifies puja type (e.g. `surya-puja`) |
| `pujaName` | String | Display name |
| `name / email / phone` | String | User details |
| `address / gotra` | String | Optional devotee info |
| `bookingDate` | String (`YYYY-MM-DD`) | Date of puja |
| `startTime` | String (`HH:MM`) | Chosen start time |
| `endTime` | String (`HH:MM`) | Auto-calculated (start + 5 hrs) |
| `package` | Enum | `basic` / `standard` / `premium` |
| `amount` | Number | Price paid in ₹ |
| `status` | Enum | `pending` → `confirmed` → `completed` / `cancelled` |

