### 3. Backend — Routes
**`server/routes/pujaBookingRoutes.js`**

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/puja-bookings/availability` | Public | Check date availability |
| `POST` | `/api/puja-bookings` | Public | Create new booking |
| `GET` | `/api/puja-bookings` | Protected | Admin: list all bookings |
| `PATCH` | `/api/puja-bookings/:id/status` | Protected | Admin: update status |

Registered in `server/index.js`:
```js
app.use('/api/puja-bookings', require('./routes/pujaBookingRoutes'));
```

