## Future Extensibility

> [!TIP]
> To add more individual puja pages (e.g. Chandra Puja), simply:
> 1. Create `ChandraPujaPage.jsx` + CSS
> 2. Add route `<Route path="/puja/chandra-puja" .../>`
> 3. Add `slug: "chandra-puja"` to the Chandra Puja entry in `Navbar.jsx mockPujas`. The dropdown link will automatically redirect!

> [!NOTE]
> **Payment Integration:** Currently the form collects the package & amount but does not process payment. To integrate Razorpay:  
> Add a Razorpay order creation step after booking validation and before `PujaBooking.create()` in the controller.
